{
  "_comment": "Demo + benchmark tenants for loop46 development. Consumed by `loop46 seed --manifest <this>`. Each `files` entry maps a `path` (where it lives in the tenant's deployment) to a `source` (where to read the bytes; resolved relative to this manifest file's directory). The `domains` list registers explicit aliases via tenant.assignDomain — for default `{id}.{public_suffix}` resolution you don't need any. `seed_kv` writes string-valued KV pairs to the tenant's app.db before workers open it.",
  "tenants": [
    {
      "id": "acme",
      "domains": ["acme.test"],
      "files": [
        {"path": "index.mjs", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/acme/index.mjs"},
        {"path": "api/index.mjs", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/acme/api/index.mjs"},
        {"path": "users/index.mjs", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/acme/users/index.mjs"},
        {"path": "cbfire/index.mjs", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/acme/cbfire/index.mjs"},
        {"path": "cbresult.mjs", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/acme/cbresult.mjs"},
        {"path": "httpfire/index.mjs", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/acme/httpfire/index.mjs"},
        {"path": "httpresult.mjs", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/acme/httpresult.mjs"},
        {"path": "heldsync/index.mjs", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/acme/heldsync/index.mjs"},
        {"path": "heldsync/onresult.mjs", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/acme/heldsync/onresult.mjs"},
        {"path": "cfg/index.mjs", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/acme/cfg/index.mjs"},
        {"path": "_config/oauth/google.json", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/acme/_config/oauth/google.json", "content_type": "application/json"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Target tenant for scripts/replay_wasm_smoke.py — exercises 4 of the 5 captured tape channels (kv, date, math_random, crypto_random) in a single handler with a non-trivial call tree (rollDie, bumpCount, fmtSalt) and a `/throw` path that fires THROW. ID matches the subdomain (replay-demo) so the *.{public_suffix} wildcard route auto-binds: replay-demo.loop46.localhost AND replay-demo.loop46.com both resolve without an explicit assignDomain.",
      "id": "replay-demo",
      "files": [
        {"path": "index.mjs", "source": "loop46-demo-tenants/replay_demo/index.mjs"}
